<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4">Welcome</h1>
    <p>Learn about <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/aspnet/core">building Web apps with ASP.NET Core</a>.</p>
    <div>
        <div class="Intro">
            <h2>Getting started</h2>
            <p>ASP.NET Core is a cross-platform, high-performance, open-source framework for building modern, cloud-based, Internet-connected applications. With ASP.NET Core, you can:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Build web apps and services, IoT apps, and mobile backends.</li>
                <li>Use your favorite development tools on Windows, macOS, and Linux.</li>
                <li>Deploy to the cloud or on-premises.</li>
                <li>Run on .NET Core or .NET Framework.</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Getting started with ASP.NET Core is easy. Just follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><a href="https://dot.net/core">Install the .NET Core SDK</a>.</li>
                <li>Create a new project with <code>dotnet new</code>.</li>
                <li>Build your project with <code>dotnet build</code>.</li>
                <li>Run your project with <code>dotnet run</code>.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
